def timeline_map_zrs() -> Timeline:
    tl = Timeline()
    for i in range(2008, 2018):
        map0 = (
            Map()
            .add(
                "", list(zip(list(df_zrs..unique()),list(df_zrs["{}".format(i)]))), "world",is_map_symbol_show = False
            )
            .set_series_opts(label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False))
            .set_global_opts(
                title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title="{}".format(i)),
                visualmap_opts=opts.VisualMapOpts(min_= 0,
                                                  max_= df_zrs["2017"].max(),
                                                  series_index=0),
            )
        )
        
        tl.add(map0,"{}".format(i))
    return tl

def timeline_scatter() -> Timeline:
    x = list(df_man.)
    tl = Timeline()
    for i in range(2008, 2018):
        scatter = (
            Scatter()
            .add_xaxis(x)
            .add_yaxis("", list(df_woman["{}".format(i)]))
            .add_yaxis("", list(df_man["{}".format(i)]))
            .set_global_opts(title_opts=opts.TitleOpts("{}".format(i)),
                             datazoom_opts=opts.DataZoomOpts(orient="vertical"),
                             visualmap_opts=opts.VisualMapOpts(
                                 type_="type",
                                 min_= 0,
                                 max_=df_man["2008"].max(),
                                 series_index=0))
            .set_series_opts(
            label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False),
        )
        )
        tl.add(scatter, "{}".format(i))
    return tl

def timeline_bar() -> Timeline:
    x = list(df_man.)
    tl = Timeline()
    for i in range(2008, 2018):
        bar = (
            Bar()
            .add_xaxis(x)
            .add_yaxis("", list(df_woman["{}".format(i)]))
            .add_yaxis("", list(df_man["{}".format(i)]))
            .reversal_axis()
            .set_global_opts(title_opts=opts.TitleOpts("{}".format(i)),
                            datazoom_opts=opts.DataZoomOpts(orient="vertical",range_start="50",range_end="60"))
            .set_series_opts(
            label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False),
        )
        )
        tl.add(bar, "{}".format(i))
    return tl

def timeline_scatter() -> Timeline:
    x = list(df_man.)
    tl = Timeline()
    for i in range(2008, 2018):
        scatter = (
            Scatter()
            .add_xaxis(x)
            .add_yaxis("", list(df_woman["{}".format(i)]))

                             visualmap_opts=opts.VisualMapOpts(

                                 min_= 0,
                                 max_=df_man["2008"].max(),

            .set_series_opts(
            label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False),
        )

from pyecharts import options as opts
from pyecharts.charts import Bar, Grid, Line, Scatter, Page

x = [int(x) for x in df0.columns.values[1:]]
x_zx = [str(x) for x in x]

def line_base1() -> Line:
    c = (
        Line()
        .add_xaxis(x_zx)
        .add_yaxis("Morocco", list(df0.loc["Morocco"].values)[1:])
        .add_yaxis("Lesotho", list(df0.loc["Lesotho"].values)[1:])
        .add_yaxis("Uganda", list(df0.loc["Uganda"].values)[1:])
        .add_yaxis("Finland", list(df0.loc["Finland"].values)[1:11])
        .add_yaxis("Australia", list(df0.loc["Australia"].values)[1:])
        .add_yaxis("United States", list(df0.loc["United States"].values)[1:])
        .add_yaxis("Pakistan", list(df0.loc["Pakistan"].values)[1:])
        .add_yaxis("Portugal", list(df0.loc["Portugal"].values)[1:])
        .add_yaxis("Sweden", list(df0.loc["Sweden"].values)[1:])
        .add_yaxis("Ireland", list(df0.loc["Ireland"].values)[1:])
        .set_global_opts(title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title="", subtitle=""),
                        legend_opts=opts.LegendOpts(pos_left="30%"))
        .set_series_opts(
            label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False),
        )
    )
    return c


def line_base2() -> Line:
    c = (
        Line()
        .add_xaxis(x_zx)
        .add_yaxis("Morocco", list(df2.loc["Morocco"].values)[1:])

x = list(df4_1.columns[2:])

def bar_reversal_axis() -> Bar:
    c = (
        Bar()
        .add_xaxis(x)
        .add_yaxis("Ireland",list(df4_1.loc['Ireland'].values[1:]))
        .add_yaxis("Iceland",list(df4_1.loc['Iceland'].values[1:]))
        .add_yaxis("Germany",list(df4_1.loc['Germany'].values[1:]))
        .add_yaxis("Turkey",list(df4_1.loc['Turkey'].values[1:]), is_selected=False)
        .add_yaxis("Portugal",list(df4_1.loc['Portugal'].values[1:]), is_selected=False)
        .add_yaxis("Luxembourg",list(df4_1.loc['Luxembourg'].values[1:]), is_selected=False)
        .add_yaxis("Finland",list(df4_1.loc['Finland'].values[1:]), is_selected=False)
        .add_yaxis("Sweden",list(df4_1.loc['Sweden'].values[1:]), is_selected=False)
        .add_yaxis("Slovenia",list(df4_1.loc['Slovenia'].values[1:]), is_selected=False)
        .add_yaxis("United Kingdom",list(df4_1.loc['United Kingdom'].values[1:]), is_selected=False)
        .set_series_opts(label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(position="top"))
        .set_global_opts(title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title=""),
                         datazoom_opts=opts.DataZoomOpts(),
                        legend_opts=opts.LegendOpts(pos_left="50%"))
    )
    return c

 = bar_reversal_axis()
.render_notebook()

def timeline_map_fn() -> Timeline:
    tl = Timeline()
    for i in range(2006, 2016):
        map0 = (
            Map()
            .add(
                "", list(zip(list(df_fn..unique()),list(df_fn["{}".format(i)]))), "world",is_map_symbol_show = False
            )
            .set_series_opts(label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False))
            .set_global_opts(
                title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title="{}".format(i)),
                visualmap_opts=opts.VisualMapOpts(min_= 0,
                                                  max_= 8,
                                                  series_index=0),
            )
        )
        
        tl.add(map0,"{}".format(i))
    return tl

Timeline_map_fn = timeline_map_fn()
Timeline_map_fn.render_notebook()

def timeline_map_gdp() -> Timeline:
    tl = Timeline()
    for i in range(2008, 2018):
        map0 = (
            Map()
            .add(
                "GDP", list(zip(list(df_gdp..unique()),list(df_gdp["{}".format(i)]))), "world",is_map_symbol_show = False
            )
            .set_series_opts(label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False))
            .set_global_opts(
                title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title="{}GDP".format(i)),
                visualmap_opts=opts.VisualMapOpts(min_= 0,
                                                  max_= df_gdp["2017"].max(),
                                                  series_index=0),
            )
        )
        
        tl.add(map0,"{}".format(i))
    return tl

Timeline_map_gdp = timeline_map_gdp()
Timeline_map_gdp.render_notebook()
